                     <interp inst="t18030525-54-person391" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn. - I am an officer belonging to Great Marlborough-street; I was sent for on the 16th to apprehend the prisoner; I did so, at her mistress's house, Mrs. Thompson's; she gave her mistress the duplicate.(The articles were produced, and identified by the prosecutrix.) <rs id="t18030525-54-verdict302" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18030525-54-verdict302" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>, aged 27.</p>
